customScript:
select
	cast(TC.OBJID as text) AS interactionChannelKey,
	CASE TC.ACTIVE
	  WHEN 0 THEN 'NO'
	  WHEN 1 THEN 'YES'
	  ELSE 'YES'
	END as activeFlag,
	CASE TC.INBOUND_IND
	  WHEN 0 THEN 'NO'
	  WHEN 1 THEN 'YES'
	  ELSE 'YES'
	END as inboundFlag,
	TC.DESCRIPTION as interactionChannelDesc,
	TM.TITLE as interactionChannelMediumInd,
	TC.TITLE as interactionChannelName,
	TC.OBJID AS interactionChannelSourceId,
	CASE TC.OUTBOUND_IND
	  WHEN 0 THEN 'NO'
	  WHEN 1 THEN 'YES'
	  ELSE 'YES'
	END as outboundFlag,
	null as sourceSystemId -- N/A
FROM TABLE_CHANNEL TC
LEFT OUTER JOIN TABLE_MEDIUM TM 
	ON TC.CHANNEL2MEDIUM = TM.OBJID;
